\begin_inset Formula $\check{h}_{\pm}^{2}$
\end_inset

 solutions is appropriate to the application at hand.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For a given solution, 
\begin_inset Formula $\check{h}^{2}$
\end_inset

, representing one of the 
\begin_inset Formula $\check{h}_{\pm}^{2}$
\end_inset

, equation
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
